<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="other-adj">other <strong><em>adj</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /'ʌðə(r)/    美 /'ʌðər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(两个中) 另一的：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>the other / one’s other + 单数名词：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He walked to the other side of the street.
他走向街对面。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Where’s my other shoe?
我的另一只鞋在哪儿？</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(多个中) 另外的；其他的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I still have other problems to solve.
我还有另外一些问题要解决。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have no <strong>other</strong> choice <strong>than</strong> this.
除此之外我别无选择。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I like dogs better than any other animal(s).
我喜欢狗胜过其他任何动物。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>the other + 复数名词：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mary is much brighter than all the other students in her class.
玛丽比她班上其他的同学聪明得多。</p></div>

<p>注: “other + 单数名词” 之前必须有one, any, some, no等词修饰，口语中也可用复数名词。  </p>
<h4 id="3">3.<strong>隔一个的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>every other day
每隔一天</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="other-than">other than</h3>
<p>1.<strong>除…以外 (except)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I don’t know any French people other than you.
除了你，我不认识别的法国人。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We are going away in June but other than that I’ll be here all summer.
我们六月份外出，除此之外，我整个夏天都会在这里。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The form cannot be signed by anyone <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (除了) yourself.  （2011 全国改）  </li>
<li>I’ll spend half of my holiday practising English and <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ half learning drawing.  （2010 全国改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. other than / except  2. the other  </p></div>